    • launchbrowser

      public org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver launchbrowser() throws InterruptedException
      This method 'launchbrowser' is used to launch browser as per the mentioned browser in config.properties Browser support - chrome, firefox, ie There are option exposed in config.properties file for Chrome browser like: requireIncognito(set as Y) - If you want to launch the browser in incognito, requireHeadless(set as Y) - If you want to launch the browser in headless mode, existingBrowserWindow(set as Y) - If you want to execute test case in existing browser. Note :In order to use existingBrowserWindow, launch the chrome browser before execution at port 4444 Use below command in cmd prompt- Step 1 : cd C:\Program Files\Google\Chrome\Application Step 2 : chrome.exe --remote-debugging-port=4444
      Returns:
      WebDriver : Returns the driver instantiated
      Throws:
      InterruptedException
